(&#123;d&#125;%)&apos;,//引导线显示格式</span><br><span class="line">                textStyle : &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                           fontWeight : &apos;normal&apos;,</span><br><span class="line">                           fontSize : 15//引导线字体大小</span><br><span class="line">                            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      </span><br><span class="line">            &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            emphasis: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                show: true,</span><br><span class="line">                textStyle: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    fontSize: &apos;30&apos;,</span><br><span class="line">                    fontWeight: &apos;bold&apos;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;//鼠标悬浮在上面字体和图表放大</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">        labelLine: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            normal: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                show: true</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;,//true:显示引导线</span><br><span class="line">        data:[</span><br><span class="line">            &#123;value:335, name:&apos;A&apos;&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            &#123;value:310, name:&apos;B&apos;&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            &#123;value:234, name:&apos;C&apos;&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            &#123;value:135, name:&apos;D&apos;&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            &#123;value:1548, name:&apos;E&apos;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        ]//数据可从后台获取，以arr.push(value:XXX;name:XXX)格式。legend的data按照以上格式;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">]&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre><h3 id="二、柱状图与曲线图结合"><a href="#二、柱状图与曲线图结合" class="headerlink" title="二、柱状图与曲线图结合"></a>二、柱状图与曲线图结合</h3><p><a href="http://ech